      • run

        public abstract int run(MemoryMap map,
      int cmd,
      int m1,
      int i1,
      int m2,
      int i2,
      int size,
      int line)
        Runs a instruction with the given arguments. m1 and i1 together are Parameter 1 m2 and i2 together are Parameter 2 size defines how this instruction is handled
        Parameters:
        map - The emulated MemoryMap
        cmd - command integer
        m1 - mode for i1
        i1 - number parameter 1
        m2 - mode for i2
        i2 - number parameter 2
        size - operation size for this instruction (byte,word,dword)
        line - the current IP
        Returns:
        the new IP
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - something went wrong
